node.text:
Ayyyyy! It’s Finally Friday! Well, there are always days where you decide to fancy up your meal & @saveursg is there for those days!

Whether you’re craving for foie gras or a whole chicken, it can all be found on their online food delivery store shop.saveur.sg that has island wide delivery! 😆 Besides food from @saveursg, you can also get some steaks from @mediumraresg or some tapas from the @frapasbar or even ice-cream from @breadandbutterflysg! 🤤

If your cravings have been awoken, it’s time to act but WAIT- I’ve got a nifty little promo code ‘GELLY10OFF’ that gets you 10% off on your order! It’s only valid in May & June so do take note! 😉

Well, that’s all I have for ya’ll! Do remember to stay home, stay safe & stay healthy! 💕
.
